nodes.text: A dark-skinned Human served as the Senator of the planet Eriadu to the Galactic Senate around 33 BBY. That year, Palpatine of Naboo proposed to organize a summit on Eriadu to discuss the taxation of Free Trade Zones, and his Eriaduan colleague answered his homeworld would be honored to host this event. Like the other members of his delegation, the senator wore loose-fitting clothes and covered his head with a turban.
